{
  "stem": "304.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I would love to have in school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But I cannot take you because you are Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So I couldn't go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And my-- OK, I have to go back with  one thing, that under the Hungarians, a lot of rules came against the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "One of them-- first of all, they took away all the-- all the government positions from people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Then, they took away the radios, the bicycles.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Every time something new came out, the men were-- the young men were drafted not in the army, but in the-- they call it [NON-ENGLISH], forced labor camps.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They-- they wear their clothes, their own civilian clothes, but they had to wear a yellow armband.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And they were taken to the frontiers to-- to work for the-- for the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They didn't fight the enemy, they were enemies too for the Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But they were doing the digging for the-- for the-- no-- for the soldiers, where they hide.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I forgot--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Fox holes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Fox holes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And to serve them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they-- they suffered hunger and-- and-- and-- and cold.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when they were taken, very seldom did we hear from them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we never knew if those-- those people were-- were alive or not.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[DRINKS] And then gradually, they took away all the businesses.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when they took away the businesses from everybody, suddenly we saw our neighbors, or people with whom we grew up, or my parents grew up, they just moved in, and different businesses.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we realized how they looked at our Jewish business before.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because they moved in and businesses already with merchandise without paying a penny.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They-- they just took it over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we didn't get paid for it anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So life became very difficult.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
